  activeProps:
  - prop: 8
    unlockTarget: 5
  propMaterialOverrides: []
  introLines:
  - I'm losing precious market hours right now. Let's make a deal
  - How much does a ticket to heaven cost? I have cash on hand
  answerWhatHappenedBefore: I was putting up a massive, high-visibility wooden billboard
    over my lemonade stand. The wind caught it, the structural support snapped, and
    the whole thing collapsed right on top of my inventory.
  answerWhatKindOfLife: Efficient and highly scalable. I drove the neighborhood kids
    out of business by undercutting their prices using cheap powdered mix instead
    of real lemons
  answerWhatWasYourJob: I was the CEO and sole shareholder of Penny's Premium Refreshments.
    I controlled the entire block's beverage market
  answerWhatHappenedClothes: My shirt has a few yellow stains on it. It's an operational
    hazard when you are mixing bulk batches of lemonade product
  answerWhyHaveItem: Money makes the world go 'round, even in this place. I brought
    this handful of quarters to secure a premium tier spot in the afterlife
